<p class="head">M<sup>r</sup> Ch<sup>s</sup> MacKenzies's <span class="DelHand-author">fourth</span> <span class="DelHand-author"><span class="AddHand-author">third</span></span><span class="AddHand-author"> second</span> Journey to the</p>
